WikifierOutput.InputText: CRICKET- AUSTRALIA WIN TOSS AND CHOOSE TO BAT. Teams: Australia- Ian Healy( captain), Michael Bevan, Damien Flemming, Jason Gillespie, Stuart Law, Glenn McGrath, Ricky Ponting, Michael Slater, Darren Lehmann, Mark Waugh, Steve Waugh.
